
<purchabr>DEAK</purchabr> BUYS <acqabr>JOHNSON MATTHEY COMMODITIES</acqabr>
    NEW YORK, APRIL 1 - <purchaser>Deak International</purchaser>, a foreign currency
and precious metals firm, announced the acquisition of <acquired>Johnson
Matthey Commodities of New York</acquired> from <seller>Minories Finance Limited</seller>,
